data.description: Nicely updated brick & stone ranch with open plan. Custom features include arched doorways, crown molding, rounded drywall edges, trey ceilings. New roof, furnace, interior paint, & luxury vinyl plank floors throughout. Updated kitchen with new granite counter tops, stainless appliances, & cabinet hardware. Master bath & hall bath has new granite vanity tops and new antique brass light fixtures and faucets. Enjoy BBQ with friends & family on wood deck and peaceful backyard.The living room/dining area is Reality Staged (virtual). Design services are offered if the buyer would like to purchase the furnishings.
